DevOps is a combination of development and operations team, which can be processed for faster deployment and delivery basically its shorten the development life cycle
Devops Automation: the addition of technology that performs tasks with reduced human assistance to processes that facilitate feedback loops between operations and development teams so that iterative updates can be deployed faster to applications in production.
Devops scaling: an automation-driven environment where developers or enterprises can adopt DevOps culture and choose the right technologies to scale their business growth.

Devops infastructure: Devops help in the automation of infrastructure and this saves the hassle and effort of having to do everything manually wich can slow down the process
 Why Devops is important ??
 Devops is important because its a software development and operations approach that enables faster development of new products and easier maintenance of existing deployment
